the laundry expenses

00:03.873 --> 00:05.831
for our residents have doubled
in the last few months.

00:05.875 --> 00:07.181
Soup.

00:07.224 --> 00:08.138
I'm sorry?

00:08.182 --> 00:09.748
We gotta serve less soup.

00:09.792 --> 00:11.315
Problem solved.

00:11.359 --> 00:13.752
Teamwork makes the dream work.

00:13.796 --> 00:16.407
[phone rings]

00:16.451 --> 00:17.974
Hold on a sec.
Uh-huh.

00:18.018 --> 00:19.454
Hey.GABBY: A guy named Scott

00:19.497 --> 00:21.325
is calling you.
He says he's a lawyer.

00:21.369 --> 00:24.198
Okay.He's a Leo with rising Gemini.

00:24.241 --> 00:26.591
They're supposed to be chatty,
but not this one.

00:26.635 --> 00:27.723
Put him through.

00:27.766 --> 00:30.073
I'm so sorry,
but I have to take this.

00:30.117 --> 00:32.162
Okay.

00:32.206 --> 00:34.077
Like, alone.

00:34.121 --> 00:35.861
Oh.

00:35.905 --> 00:37.602
And do you mind closing
the door on your way out?

00:37.646 --> 00:38.647
Hey.

00:38.690 --> 00:39.735
If you've got
something to hide,

00:39.778 --> 00:41.476
none of my business.

00:43.913 --> 00:44.827
Do your hands hurt?

00:44.870 --> 00:45.958
Constantly.

00:46.002 --> 00:47.221
What do you do about it?

00:47.264 --> 00:49.049
Well, I try and focus
on the part of me

00:49.092 --> 00:50.354
that doesn't hurt.

00:50.398 --> 00:52.574
Which is this area right there.

00:54.880 --> 00:55.838
May I join you?

00:55.881 --> 00:57.405
Course.

01:01.148 --> 01:03.019
Is everything okay?

01:03.063 --> 01:04.238
Not sure.

01:04.281 --> 01:05.891
Ooh, tell us, tell us.

01:05.935 --> 01:07.763
Gina was in her office

01:07.806 --> 01:08.851
with the door closed

01:08.894 --> 01:10.157
talking to a lawyer.

01:10.200 --> 01:11.288
About what?

01:11.332 --> 01:14.291
She made me leave the room.

01:15.249 --> 01:17.512
So something she didn't
want you to hear.

01:17.555 --> 01:22.343
Wow, I can see why
you were such a good cop.

01:22.386 --> 01:24.040
I heard her complaining
that running this place

01:24.084 --> 01:25.607
was tougher than she thought.

01:25.650 --> 01:27.826
Did she say she wanted to sell?

01:27.870 --> 01:28.914
No, not to me.

01:28.958 --> 01:30.568
Oh, she wouldn't
sell this place.

01:30.612 --> 01:33.136
Although you certainly have
made her life very difficult.

01:33.180 --> 01:34.224
What did I do?

01:34.268 --> 01:35.791
Demanding that English be

01:35.834 --> 01:37.488
the official language
of Valley Hills!

01:37.532 --> 01:39.229
You're the one always
bugging her about

01:39.273 --> 01:40.709
getting almond milk.

01:40.752 --> 01:44.016
If it doesn't come
from a cow, it's not milk.

01:44.060 --> 01:45.192
Then what is it?

01:45.235 --> 01:47.977
A liberal conspiracy
to poison America.

01:48.804 --> 01:51.415
Hey! What's shakin',
eggs and bacon?

01:53.765 --> 01:56.333
Am I not as adorable
as I thought?

01:56.377 --> 01:58.248
Gina, please
don't leave us.

01:58.292 --> 01:59.423
We promise we'll be better.

01:59.467 --> 02:00.511
What are you talking about?

02:00.555 --> 02:01.904
We don't have to speak English.

02:01.947 --> 02:03.862
We can habla español.

02:03.906 --> 02:05.777
And I'll drink regular milk.

02:05.821 --> 02:08.998
Apologies to those
who sit near me.

02:09.041 --> 02:11.609
These shmendricks have
gotten it into their head

02:11.653 --> 02:13.307
that you're selling
Valley Hills.

02:13.350 --> 02:15.091
You got a call
from a lawyer.

02:15.135 --> 02:17.615
[laughs]:
Oh... that.

02:17.659 --> 02:21.228
No. It's some legal trouble
from when I was younger.

02:21.271 --> 02:22.881
I'm trying to find an attorney.

02:22.925 --> 02:24.274
[relieved sighing]

02:24.318 --> 02:27.582
I told 'em it was nothing
to worry about.

02:27.625 --> 02:31.455
People just love to gossip.

